about.summary: Various objects to denote special meanings in python

name: sentinels
raw_recipe:
{%set name = "sentinels" %}
{%set version = "1.0.0" %}
{%set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{%set hash_val = "7be0704d7fe1925e397e92d18669ace2f619c92b5d4eb21a89f31e026f9ff4b1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  {{ hash_type }}: {{ hash_val }}

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - sentinels

about:
  home: https://github.com/vmalloc/sentinels
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  license_family: BSD
  summary: 'Various objects to denote special meanings in python'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pmlandwehr
